RL_OTC_MASTER_INVOCE.@EndUserText.label: Master Invoice Master Report
RL_OTC_MASTER_INVOCE.@DataWarehouse.sqlEditor.query:
SELECT distinct "bill"."VBELN",
                "bill"."BUKRS",
--                "bill"."POSNR",
                "bill"."VGBEL",
--                "bill"."VGPOS",
                "bill"."KUNAG",
 --               "hu"."VENUM",
 --               "hu"."EXIDV",
 --               "hu"."VBELN" as "VBELN1", 
                "hu"."DOC_NUMBER",
 --              "hu"."POSNR" as "POSNR1",
               "hu"."BOLNR",
  --              "hu"."CA_WDATU",
                "hu"."CA_PONUMB",
                "hu"."TDLNR",
                "hu"."INHALT" as "Tracking ID",
                "hu"."WERKS",
                "del"."KUNNR",
                "del"."WADAT_IST",
                 1 as "counter"

FROM (
                                SELECT DISTINCT "VBELN",
                                                "BUKRS",
                                                "POSNR", 
                                            "AUBEL",
                                             "AUPOS",
                                                "VGBEL",
                                                 "VGPOS",
                                                "KUNAG"
                                FROM "TD_STG.HL_OTC_BILLING_ITM_01"
--WHERE "AUBEL"='1000025923'
                ) as "bill"


join (
select DISTINCT "VBELN","POSNR","KUNNR","WADAT_IST","VGBEL","VGPOS"
 from "TD_STG.HL_OTC_DELIVERY_ITM_01" )AS del
  ON "del"."VBELN" = "bill"."VGBEL" AND "del"."VGBEL"="bill"."AUBEL" AND "del"."VGPOS"="bill"."AUPOS"
 --AND "del"."POSNR" = "bill"."VGPOS"
           

                JOIN (
                                SELECT DISTINCT "VENUM",
                                                "EXIDV",
                                                "VBELN" ,
                                                "DOC_NUMBER",
                                                "POSNR" ,
                                                "BOLNR",
--                                                "CA_WDATU",
                                                "CA_PONUMB",
                                                "TDLNR",
                                                "INHALT",
                                                "WERKS" 
                                FROM "TD_STG.HL_OTC__HANDLING_UNIT"
--where "VBELN"='8000004974'
                ) as "hu" ON "hu"."VBELN" = "del"."VBELN" AND "hu"."POSNR" = "del"."POSNR"
